ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectMission Chamber of Commerce (British Columbia) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the MISSION CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in British Columbia, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the judicial district of New Westminster to 287th Street (East) to Morris Valley Road (West), and to the Fraser River North (to the North end of Stave Lake).
